(6568, 1850, 771, 1, 'Something''s aint right', '', '2005-12-31 00:00:00', 0000, 15, 0, 4, 'Something right 詞/曲:小玉\r\n\r\nYeah,when I was a bad child.\r\nPapa gave me a guitar.\r\nIt''s the way that he can show me his love.\r\nI played it as well as I can.\r\nSang with all my creation.\r\nBut when I grow up,still pissed him off.\r\n\r\nSomething''s aint right,but still go on.\r\nChanging seems like the way I have to accept.\r\nBut I think it''s all right.\r\nCuz I left it all behind.\r\n\r\nOne day I meet a pretty honey.\r\nI led her to my playground.\r\nShow how much I love her I wrote this song.\r\nBut she tells me it''s nothing.\r\nWe''re together just for fun.\r\nAfter wiping my tears and she''s gone.\r\n\r\nSomething''s aint right,but still go on.\r\nChanging seems like the way I have to accept.\r\nBut I think it''s all right.\r\nCuz I left it all behind.\r\n\r\nI know it would be hurt.but\r\nI never been taught to give up.\r\nI should believe this ground I stand is where bleesed.\r\nthough seperation I learn about love.\r\nAnd it made me cry out loud.\r\nThen the pain never really stop at all.\r\n\r\nI''ve dreamed of a carnival for me.\r\nThan lost it cuz you kick me.\r\nStill mess around like before.\r\nI''ve got to figure out the answer once more.\r\nBut I don''t wanna realize.\r\n\r\nSomething''s aint right,but still go on.\r\nChanging seems like the way I have to accept.\r\nBut I think it''s all right.\r\nCuz I left it all behind.\r\n\r\nI know it would be hurt.but\r\nI never been taught to give up.\r\nSuch a depreesion occupy my life time.', '', 288, '', '小玉', '小玉', 'D.Y.', '', '', 0, 0, 0, '2008-07-02 17:14:15', '2015-03-12 13:33:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
